OL,4,CHSBC boss Noel Quinn scraps executive
OL,5,Cfloor at London HQ
OL,6, Banking giant HSBC has confirmed that
OL,7, top managers in its Canary Wharf HQ
OL,8, have lost their offices and will have
OL,9, to hot-desk on an open-plan floor.
OL,11,FIt comes as HSBC pursues plans to
OL,12,Fshrink its office space by 40% in a
OL,13,Fpost-pandemic shake-up.
OL,15,FBoss Noel Quinn said the whole bank was
OL,16,Fembracing "hybrid working" and he would
OL,17,Fno longer come in five days a week.
OL,19,F"My leadership team and I have moved to
OL,20,Fa fully open-plan floor with no
OL,21,Fdesignated desks," he said on Linkedin.
